  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slingbot Survivors</strong> is a roguelike auto-shooter with physics-based platforming. Explore a hostile alien planet, use your grappling hook to zip around, and wield an arsenal of powerful weapons & gadgets to wipe out hordes of alien horrors!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot, swing & pull!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your versatile grappling hook to outmaneuver your enemies, find resources scattered throughout the environment, and fly around in supersonic speeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Only the best can truly master the art of recklessly throwing yourself at your foes.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your own Sling-Bot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield a vast array of unique weapons, upgrade their stats to suit your build, and <i>customize</i> them with unique<strong> </strong>augments that change their behavior & playstyle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together with special gadgets that grant unique passive abilities, and a variety of different Sling-Bots to play with, each run you can devise new exciting ways to rain down fire upon your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Warning: Legs not included.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive a hostile alien planet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From masses of angry <i>Biters</i> to hulking, charging<i> Swarm-Guards</i>, each enemy the planet throws at you poses a unique challenge to overcome on your quest to pave out a new home for humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just watch out, you don't want to become worm-food!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join our Discord</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to report any bugs or share your feedback, be sure to check out our Discord channel! You can chat with the dev team, see what's going on behind the scenes, or just hang around with your fellow Intergalactic Bug-Squashers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slingbot Survivors</strong> is a roguelike auto-shooter with physics-based platforming. Explore a hostile alien planet, use your grappling hook to zip around, and wield an arsenal of powerful weapons & gadgets to wipe out hordes of alien horrors!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shoot, swing & pull!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your versatile grappling hook to outmaneuver your enemies, find resources scattered throughout the environment, and fly around in supersonic speeds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/a4508bed66ee36978601af25783859f2.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Only the best can truly master the art of recklessly throwing yourself at your foes.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build your own Sling-Bot</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wield a vast array of unique weapons, upgrade their stats to suit your build, and <i>customize</i> them with unique<strong> </strong>augments that change their behavior & playstyle! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together with special gadgets that grant unique passive abilities, and a variety of different Sling-Bots to play with, each run you can devise new exciting ways to rain down fire upon your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=656 height=368 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/47d22d452814f2c10102c3da5576f4a5.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Warning: Legs not included.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survive a hostile alien planet</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From masses of angry <i>Biters</i> to hulking, charging<i> Swarm-Guards</i>, each enemy the planet throws at you poses a unique challenge to overcome on your quest to pave out a new home for humanity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.poster.avif?t=1774490021\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.webm?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432800/extras/d8353f03254846de5d7b6f07249eea82.mp4?t=1774490021\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Just watch out, you don't want to become worm-food!</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Join our Discord</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you want to report any bugs or share your feedback, be sure to check out our Discord channel! You can chat with the dev team, see what's going on behind the scenes, or just hang around with your fellow Intergalactic Bug-Squashers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
